net.sf.mpxj.primavera.common

Class MapRow

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mpxj.primavera.common.MapRow

  • public class MapRow
extends Object
    Wraps a simple map which contains name value pairs representing the column values from an individual row. Provides type-specific methods to retrieve the column values.
